 --------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 EPS Growth %         P/E 1992
                              1991*      1992       Sept       Dec
Canada - TSE                 -21.9       53.5        13         15
France - CAC 40               -2.7       15.7        15         11
Germany - Dax                  1.5        7.2        13         13
Italy - BCI                   -6.7       15.3        12         14
Japan - Nikkei                -6.4        4.0        37         38
UK - FTSE                     -9.8       26.2        12         12
US - S&amp;P 500                 -11.4       30.0        13         15
