         US LIGHT VEHICLE SALES 1991
 --------------------------------------------------
         units    %age     market change
                 share
GM       4.346m   -12.6        35.1%
Ford     2.899m   -13.8        23.3%
Chrysler 1,508m   -11.2        12.2%
