market crash and dollar weakness - was generally expected in view of the
recession in the US and the problems of the motor sector in North America.
Porsche will next week spell out details of its performance at its annual
press conference near Stuttgart. It has already said that net profits in its
financial year to July 31 1991 fell to less than DM60m (Dollars 39m) from
