Dollars 4.2m by January 1996.
In the 12 months to September 30 1991, Perma Pure achieved pre-tax profits
of Dollars 220,000 on turnover of Dollars 3.24m. Asset value at acquisition
was about Dollars 1m.
</TEXT>
