 -----------------------------
                Exc.    Inc.
               grants  grants
1986-87          8.1     6.3
1987-88          8.4     5.4
1988-89         10.3     7.4
1989-90          7.7     5.3
1990-91          8.0     5.6
1991-92          6.0     4.0
